<br />\n但都想佢陪下 不過唔洗每次<br />\n佢自己搭都好悶<br />\n可能五次入面一兩次都ok</blockquote><br />\n姐係女仔會覺得男仔咁做warm???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申唔識摸你地女仔心態，順粹問下男仔應該點做姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3034ab2b91e479576e6a43ff8dda05d5668f490","tid":107282,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"如果唔太夜，第二日唔洗番工我男朋友會話同我搭番去。反而真係夜嘅佢唔會有送我返去嘅念頭，陪搭地鐵都唔會，因為好易冇尾班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以唔關危險事。<br />\n不過通常我都會話自己番，但佢有呢份心意，耐唔耐一次，好似上面絲打咁講五次有一次咁都幾warm。"},{"pid":"48166ee4130a00afe6c2b4c9465ab56882515a6f","tid":107282,"uid":72184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"係男人就送人地返屋企樓下，兩個鐘都咁話"},{"pid":"204ec4ec1efc6a996518ff54c69a58d3a839fb72","tid":107282,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"唔係危唔危險問題，係你會唔會為想見多20分鐘，而陪佢搭去荃灣"},{"pid":"9938fdc0fe6439b639dcb69f429657959a7c793b","tid":107282,"uid":17966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"20 分鐘都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30031b9cab169484de816d422c276c78505b34bd","tid":107282,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"你覺得好on9曬時間咪唔好送囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁既態度就好似對多陣都唔想咁<br />\n人地就爭取時間見面<br />\n你就想拿拿聲閃做自己野<br />\n應該索性分手 <br />\n等自己多d時間"},{"pid":"c109eee1629081c3b8b1a22679644a38af8e7a92","tid":107282,"uid":8020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n佢成日比人𥄫同搭訕<br />\n佢住得好近地鐵站<br />\n我會陪佢搭到嗰個站然後自己回頭車返去<br />\n當係多謝佢陪我出左成日街<br />\n利申其實係想見多佢一陣"},{"pid":"dbde32574d1320cfae9441b4d91394ddfaa16614","tid":107282,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"係尖沙咀開房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b629f3ecca6c2fac4252248dfe69336fb9618067","tid":107282,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"我男朋友淨係得一次無送，因為佢嗰日太攰，我堅持唔俾佢送。成日同佢講唔好送啦，都係十幾分鐘車程，但佢都會照送，仲要明明可以沿線搭返車返屋企，佢都會出埋閘送到我去屋企大堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我愛我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdddbc41bbe9404ccce4154e58bda2794ec10e93","tid":107282,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:07:32.000Z","msg":"有時同班fd 食完飯之後同佢一齊等巴士,佢撘個架巴士經我住嘅地方附近,而我撘個架到咗,佢無提示叫我上車或逼我上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多次我都會陪佢撘車（佢都知唔太啱我路）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,係車到有傾有講其實幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有問過駛唔駛送到佢屋企樓下,好幾次佢都話唔洗就無再問過,有無巴打教路其實係唔係做緊兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就快搬走啦,唔會再有呢d 機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：唔係男女朋友關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32f67670950d0eb0a5c8d9dc3cce323f1a55c05","tid":107282,"uid":71869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"